== 超新星 ==
在半人馬座A曾經檢測到一顆[[超新星|超新星]]<ref name="nedsn">{{cite web
  | title=NASA/IPAC Extragalactic Database
  | work=Results for extended name search on Centaurus A
  | url=http://nedwww.ipac.caltech.edu/
  | accessdate=2007-03-07
  | archive-date=2008-12-16
  | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081216032441/http://nedwww.ipac.caltech.edu/
  | dead-url=no
  }}</ref>。
這顆超新星，[[SN_1986G|SN 1986G]]，是[[羅伯特艾文思_(天文學家)|艾文思]]於1986年在塵埃帶內發現的<ref name="iauc">{{cite journal
  | author=R. Evans | author2=R. H. McNaught | author3=C. Humphries
  | title=Supernova 1986G in NGC 5128
  | journal=IAU Circular
  | date=1986
  | pages=1
  | volume=4208
  | bibcode=1986IAUC.4208....1E
  }}</ref>，
稍後被鑑定是一顆[[Ia超新星|Ia超新星]]<ref name="phillipsetal1987">{{cite journal
  | author=M. M. Phillips | display-authors=4 | author2=A. C. Phillips | author3=S. R. Heathcote | author4=V. M. Blanco | author5=D. Geisler | author6=D. Hamilton | author7=N. B. Suntzeff | author8=F. J. Jablonski | author9=J. E. Steiner | author10=A. P. Cowley | author11=P. Schmidtke | author12=S. Wyckoff | author13=J. B. Hutchings | author14=J. Tonry | author15=M. A. Strauss | author16=J. R. Thorstensen | author17=W. Honey | author18= J. Maza | author19= M. T. Ruiz | author20= A. U. Landolt | author21= A. Uomoto | author22=R. M. Rich | author23=J. E. Grindlay | author24= H. Cohn | author25=H. A. Smith | author26=J. H. Lutz | author27=R. J. Lavery | author28=A.  Saha
  | title=The type 1a supernova 1986G in NGC 5128 – Optical photometry and spectra
  | journal=Publications of the Astronomical Society of the Pacific
  | date=1987
  | volume=99
  | pages=592–605
  | bibcode=1987PASP...99..592P  | doi=10.1086/132020}}</ref>。Ia超新星通常是有一顆白矮星的[[聯星系統|聯星系統]]，白矮星由伴星攫取氣體，使質量至足以點燃在核心的碳融合反應，引發[[熱失控|熱失控]]的核融合。SN 1986G被用來演示Ia超新星的光譜並不是全都一樣，Ia超新星的光譜可能會隨著時間的推移，在亮度和形式上有不同的改變<ref name="phillipsetal1987" />。
2016年2月发现第二颗超新星SN 2016adj，稍后经被鉴定为是一颗Ⅱb超新星。

== 距離 ==
自1980年代以來，估計NGC 5128的距離通常在3-5百萬[[秒差距|秒差距]]<ref name="tonryetal2001"/><ref name="ned-dist">{{cite web|title=Distance Results for NGC 5128|work=NASA/IPAC Extragalactic Database|url=http://nedwww.ipac.caltech.edu/cgi-bin/nDistance?name=NGC+5128|accessdate=2010-04-26|archive-date=2019-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191018113525/http://ned.ipac.caltech.edu/cgi-bin/nDistance?name=NGC+5128|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=ferrarese07/><ref name=majaess10/><ref name=harris10/><ref name=rejkuba04/>。發現在NGC 5128的[[經典造父變星|經典造父變星]]受到濃厚的塵埃巷道遮蔽，依據消光法的本質和考慮其他的因素，距離估計在300-350萬秒差距<ref name=ferrarese07>{{cite journal | author = Ferrarese Laura | display-authors = 4 | author2 = Mould Jeremy R. | author3 = Stetson Peter B. | author4 = Tonry John L. | author5 = Blakeslee John P. | author6 = Ajhar Edward A. | date =2007 | title = The Discovery of Cepheids and a Distance to NGC 5128 | doi = 10.1086/506612 | bibcode=2007ApJ...654..186F | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 654 | issue = | page = 186 |arxiv = astro-ph/0605707 }}</ref><ref name=majaess10>{{cite journal|bibcode=2010AcA....60..121M|author1=Majaess, D.|date=2010|pages=121|volume=60 |title=The Cepheids of Centaurus A (NGC 5128) and Implications for H0 |journal=Acta Astronomica|arxiv = 1006.2458 }}</ref>。在NGC 5128也發現[[米拉變星|米拉變星]]<ref name=rejkuba04>{{cite journal |bibcode=2004A&A...413..903R |title=The distance to the giant elliptical galaxy NGC 5128 |journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics|arxiv = astro-ph/0310639 |doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:20034031 |date=2004 |last1=Rejkuba |first1=M. |volume=413 |issue=3 |pages=903 }}</ref>和[[第二型造父變星|第二型造父變星]]<ref name=ferrarese07/><ref name=majaess10/>，而後者很少在[[本星系群|本星系群]]之外被發現<ref name=majaess09>{{cite journal |author1=Majaess, D. |bibcode=2009AcA....59..403M |date=2009 |author2=Turner, D. |page=403 |author3=Lane, D. |title=Type II Cepheids as Extragalactic Distance Candles |volume=59 |journal=Acta Astronomica|arxiv = 0909.0181 }}</ref>。以一些[[米拉變星|米拉變星]]和[[行星狀星雲|行星狀星雲]]測定的距離，認為是更遠的〜380萬秒差距<ref name=harris10b>{{cite journal |bibcode=2010PASA...27..475H |author1=Harris, Gretchen L. H. |doi=10.1071/AS09063 |title=NGC 5128: The Giant Beneath |date=2010 |pages=475 |issue=4 |volume=27 |journal=Publications of the Astronomical Society of Australia|arxiv = 1004.4907 }}</ref><ref name=harris10>{{cite journal |doi=10.1071/AS09061 |last1=Harris |arxiv=0911.3180 |first1=Gretchen L. H. |last2=Rejkuba |first2=Marina |last3=Harris |first3=William E. |title=The Distance to NGC 5128 (Centaurus A) |journal=Publications of the Astronomical Society of Australia |volume=27 |issue=4 |pages=457–462 |date=2010|bibcode = 2010PASA...27..457H }}</ref>。


